quran[9{c,v,t}:
11,54,"hum to yeh samajte hain ke tairay oopar hamaray mabodon mein se kisi ki maar par gayi hai"" hood ne kaha"" mein Allah ki shahadat paish karta hon aur tum gawah raho ke yeh jo Allah ke siwa dosaron ko tum ne khudai mein shareektehra rakha hai is se mein bezaar hon"
11,55,tum sab ke sab mil kar mere khilaaf apni karni mein kasar nah utha rakho aur mujhe zara mohlat nah do
11,56,mera bharosa Allah par hai jo mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi koi jandaar aisa nahi jis ki chouti is ke haath mein nah ho be shak mera rab seedhi ray ah par hai
11,57,"agar tum mun phertey ho to phair lau jo pegham day kar mein tumahray paas bheja gaya tha woh mein tum ko pouncha chuka hon ab mera rab tumhari jagah doosri qoum ko uthaye ga aur tum is ka kuch nah bigaar sakuu ge yaqeenan mera rab har cheez par nigaran hai """
11,58,phir jab hamara hukum agaya to hum ne apni rehmat se hood ko aur unn logon ko jo uss ke sath imaan laaye thay nijaat day di aur aik sakht azaab se bacha liya
11,59,"yeh hain Aad , apne rab ki ayaat se unhon ne inkaar kya, is ke Rasolo-n ki baat nah maani, aur har Jabbar dushman haq ki pairwi karte rahay"
11,60,"aakhir-kaar is duniya mein bhi un par phatkaar pari aur qayamat ke roz bhi suno! Aad ne apne rab se kufar kya, suno! daur pheink diye gay Aad , hood ki qoum ke log"
11,61,"aur smod ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai saleh ko bheja uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Allah ki bandagi karo, aُ seen ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai wohi hai jis ne tum ko zameen se peda kya hai aur yahan tum ko basaayaa hai lehaza tum is se maffi chaho aur is ki taraf palat aao, yaqeenan mera rab qareeb hai aur woh duaon ka jawab dainay wala hai """
11,62,"unhon ne kaha"" ae saleh, is se pehlay to hamaray darmain aisa shakhs tha jis se barri tawaquaat wabsta theen kya to hamein un mabodon ki parastish se rokna chahta hai jin ki parastish hamaray baap dada karte thay? to jis tareeqay ki taraf hamein bulaa raha hai is ke baray mein hum ko sakht shuba hai jis ne hamein Khuljan mein daal rakha hai """
